{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"28a6fb7d-5f55-4084-90b3-06e17a15df13","content":"**You will need to change your target framework.** MSTest v4 dropped support for .NET 6.0 (and other older TFMs). It requires at minimum:\n\n- **.NET 8.0** (for library/test projects)\n- **.NET Framework 4.6.2+** (still supported)\n\nTo migrate, update your `TargetFramework` to at least `net8.0`:\n\n```xml\n<TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n```\n\nAnd update the MSTest package to v4:\n\n```xml\n<PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"4.0.0\" />\n```\n\nNote that .NET 6.0 is already out of support (EOL November 2024), so moving to `net8.0` (LTS) is recommended regardless.\n\nWould you like me to make these changes to your project?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"3da7a121-abc2-4c62-aad0-790813a1e4a6","outputTokens":211,"requestId":"BD00:2CA3BD:2028272:2462B3B:6A07D505"},"id":"b67dd2ec-3757-4606-88c2-c4dfd83545b8","timestamp":"2026-05-16T02:23:07.338Z","parentId":"b423aa2a-f65f-4175-8129-11b8d9c5923d"}
